Roadmap

# 

<span key="03fbc6588bfc4c9e9a3fb2a4dfc149a5"><span offset-key="03fbc6588bfc4c9e9a3fb2a4dfc149a5:0">Roadmap: Family Promise: Service Tracker</span></span>

## 

<span key="193c2933e0214978aec73ec10f3ff263"><span offset-key="193c2933e0214978aec73ec10f3ff263:0">Type</span></span>

<span key="19e633a621354faa856ed30143173872">**Web (Node) + DS**<span offset-key="19e633a621354faa856ed30143173872:1"> (Build-on)</span></span>

## 

<span key="a335dd6f3215428bb170ed7e4a59f9b5"><span offset-key="a335dd6f3215428bb170ed7e4a59f9b5:0">Overview</span></span>

<span key="c035af385bf042229a8ddfd7bbc8352a"><span offset-key="c035af385bf042229a8ddfd7bbc8352a:0">Family Promise helps local communities coordinate their compassion to address the root causes of family homelessness. They tap existing local resources to empower families towards economic stability. Families come to them in crisis; they help them rebuild their lives with new skills and ongoing support. They address the issue holistically, providing prevention services before families reach crisis, shelter and case management when they become homeless, and stabilization programs once they have secured housing to ensure they remain independent.</span></span>

<span key="2d27dd6d86eb49cf8c0261d514527a90"><span offset-key="2d27dd6d86eb49cf8c0261d514527a90:0">Family Promise needs a way to </span>**track and visualize the services they provide external to the shelter to gain actionable insights**<span offset-key="2d27dd6d86eb49cf8c0261d514527a90:2">.</span></span>

<span key="52fe531348b1416f93949b5b5e23e52a"><span offset-key="52fe531348b1416f93949b5b5e23e52a:0">Our goal is to build a </span>***generalizable***<span offset-key="52fe531348b1416f93949b5b5e23e52a:2"> </span>**monitoring and evaluation (M&E) platform**<span offset-key="52fe531348b1416f93949b5b5e23e52a:4"> that meets Family Promise's needs, with an eye toward additional potential use cases that would be useful for many other organizations.</span></span>

<span key="4f0e15b9e75b406a88ccbaf1ae244e0f"><span offset-key="4f0e15b9e75b406a88ccbaf1ae244e0f:0">This product will take multiple Labs cohorts to complete.</span></span>

<span key="23b45e7e1b8e4bd8a043a008f9887c3e"><span offset-key="23b45e7e1b8e4bd8a043a008f9887c3e:0">For the first round, students laid a solid foundation for the application. They built out user roles and profiles, an interface for user management, and a way for users to manage programs in the application.</span></span>

<span key="2f604e9d6de14b8cb5789d09150869b4"><span offset-key="2f604e9d6de14b8cb5789d09150869b4:0">The next round focused on ensuring individual services can be tracked for recipients at the household and individual level.</span></span>

<span key="399dfa3646aa4754bb1e6137abc8b39c"><span offset-key="399dfa3646aa4754bb1e6137abc8b39c:0">This round, we'll pick up the previous team's work building out </span>**metrics**<span offset-key="399dfa3646aa4754bb1e6137abc8b39c:2"> to serve as the main window our users will have into conducting monitoring and evaluation of their programs and services. Then we'll let Administrators and Program Managers define </span>**Goals**<span offset-key="399dfa3646aa4754bb1e6137abc8b39c:4"> based on one or more metrics, and provide </span>**analytics**<span offset-key="399dfa3646aa4754bb1e6137abc8b39c:6"> and </span>**visualizations**<span offset-key="399dfa3646aa4754bb1e6137abc8b39c:8"> to display relevant data for each user type.</span></span>
